title: Dominik Bacher
text:
Dominik Bacher (born 19 June 2002) is a German <a href="association%20football">footballer</a> who currently plays as a <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a> for <a href="TSV%201860%20Rosenheim">TSV 1860 Rosenheim</a> on loan from <a href="SpVgg%20Unterhaching">SpVgg Unterhaching</a>.
Career.
He joined <a href="TSV%201860%20Rosenheim">1860 Rosenheim</a> on loan in September 2020.
